snippet: AirTran Airways topped all United States carriers in the latest rankings for on-time arrivals, knocking off the perennial winner Hawaiian Airlines.
abstract: Transportation Dept reports AirTran Airways topped list of US carriers in latest rankings for on-time arrivals, dislodging perennial winner Hawaiian Airlines; AirTran has now been folded into Southwest Airlines.
lead_paragraph: AirTran Airways topped all United States carriers in the latest rankings for on-time arrivals, knocking off the perennial winner Hawaiian Airlines.

headline.main: Airtran Leads On-Time List in Its Final Attempt
